dcterms:description: The official dataset for the eRisk 2023 Task 1, derived from previous eRisk data, formatted in accordance with TREC guidelines. It consists of a collection of user documents, with 3,107 unique users contributing to a total of 3,807,115 sentences.
dcterms:title: eRisk 2023 Task 1 Official Dataset

dcterms:description: The 'Depression: Reddit Dataset' from Kaggle, which comprises raw data scraped from various mental health-related subreddits. The data was cleaned and processed for depression classification, containing 7,731 sentences with binary labels for depression-related content.
dcterms:title: Depression: Reddit Dataset
